title: Come Get Great Deals While They Last. Come Over Today!!
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 85', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 925-965 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Come home to Copper Creek Apartments!', "We're a secluded community that offers you the serenity of rural living while being just minutes from local shopping and freeways.", "We're affordable luxury at it's best.", 'Our designer interiors have large closets, full size washer and dryer, deluxe bathrooms, private patios, gourmet kitchens, and energy efficient gas fireplaces.', 'We also offer you a state of the art fitness center, outdoor pool and spa, community events, and covered parking!', 'We have six spacious floor plans to choose from, so let us help you make Copper Creek your home!', 'Features:', 'Washer/Dryer, Efficient Appliances, Electronic Thermostat, High Ceilings, View, Window Coverings, Large Closets, Disposal, Ceiling Fan, Extra Storage, Cable Ready, Microwave, Wheelchair Access, Fireplace, Carpeting, Refrigerator, Patio/Balcony, Dishwasher', 'Community Amenities:', 'Spa/Hot Tub, Pool, Night Patrol, Covered Parking, Recycling, Clubhouse, High Speed Internet, Package Receiving, Playground, On-Site Management, Free Weights, On-Site Maintenance, Fitness Center, Controlled Access/Gated, Carport, Sundeck', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats - 2 allowed, One time Fee $300.00, Rent $35.00, Deposit $250.00', 'Dogs - 2 allowed, One time Fee $300.00, Rent $50.00, Deposit $250.00', 'Comments: Breed Restrictions Apply', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'sx9ne0Lh']
